ogle&#39;s requirements.<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div>The module has been developed to allow you to create, step by step, a product data feed for which&nbsp;<strong>you are in control of the information<\/strong>. We have included, throughout the configuration,&nbsp;<strong>links to a precise and complete documentation<\/strong>&nbsp;based on&nbsp;<strong>Google&#39;s official regulations<\/strong>. You quickly get a clear product data file that you can export to Google Merchant Center and which you can schedule to be updated automatically at the desired frequency.<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div>New from Google: with a quality product data feed, you now have the ability to display&nbsp;<strong>for free<\/strong>&nbsp;your products on Google Shopping, and other compatible Google properties, in &quot;free product listings&quot;. Thanks to our module, which meets all Google requirements for quality and completeness of product data, you are sure to meet all eligibility criteria to use this feature, so don&#39;t hesitate any longer!<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div>Any questions? Our support department has&nbsp;<strong>many years of experience and a high level of expertise regarding the rather strict constraints and demands of Google Merchant Center,<\/strong>&nbsp;and will be happy to answer your questions in the best possible way!<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div>For even more features, such as the ability to create precise product exclusion rules, export your promotions and product reviews, or create customized segmentation of your catalog with advanced custom labels, discover <strong>the PRO version of the module<\/strong> available on https:\/\/addons.prestashop.com\/en\/price-comparison\/20908-google-merchant-center-pro-google-shopping.html<\/div>\r\n","tab":"smart_shopping","version":"4.8.9","compatibility":{"from":"1.7.6.0","to":"8.1.2"},"nbRates":"687","product_type":"module","avgRate":"4.4","price":{"EUR":18