"displayName":"Google Merchant Center PRO (Google-Shopping)","categoryName":"Price Comparison","categoryId":"490","categoryParentName":"Traffic & Marketplaces","categoryParentEnglishName":"Traffic & Marketplaces","categoryParentId":"488","description":"With Google Merchant Center (Google-Shopping) PRO, manage data export and Google Shopping segmentation in even greater precision, take part in Google Customer Reviews, export your product reviews and ","author":"Business Tech","url":"https:\/\/addons.prestashop.com\/en\/price-comparison\/20908-google-merchant-center-pro-google-shopping.html?utm_source=back-office&utm_medium=push-addons&utm_campaign=back-office-EN&utm_content=download","img":"https:\/\/medias1.prestastore.com\/img\/pico\/20908.jpg","fullDescription":"<div>With Google Merchant Center (Google-Shopping) PRO, manage data export and Google Shopping segmentation in even greater precision, take part in Google Customer Reviews, export your product reviews and special offers, display a seller rating badge\u2026<\/div>","additionalDescription":"<div><b>EVEN MORE DATA CONTROL WITH THIS PROFESSIONAL VERSION<\/b><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>With more than a decade of success, the standard version of our Google Merchant Center (Google Shopping) module is by far&nbsp;<b>the most robust and complete<\/b>&nbsp;Google Shopping module on the market.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>This&nbsp;<b>professional<\/b>&nbsp;version goes even further with&nbsp;<b>exclusive<\/b>&nbsp;features such as the ability to create precise product exclusion rules, to manage&nbsp;<b>advanced<\/b>&nbsp;custom labels, or to export your promotions and product reviews(*).<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><b>GO EVEN FURTHER IN OPTIMIZING THE DISTRIBUTION OF YOUR ADS<\/b><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>In addition to the multiple possibilities of configuring your feed that the standard version of the module already offers, you will be able to refine the choice of products or product combinations to be exported thanks to the setting up of extremely precise and personalized exclusion rules.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thanks to the advanced assignation of custom labels, you will also have the ability to segment your product catalog and therefore organize your ads according to the seasonality of your products, their popularity, or the margin you can apply to them. This allows you to control your budget by offering the right products at the right time and optimize your return on investment.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>In Shopping ads, the display of stars reflecting the rating of items undoubtedly gives more attractiveness to products.  <\/div><div>Google Merchant Center Pro allows you&nbsp;<b>to export your customers' product reviews(*)<\/b>&nbsp;and to participate in the \"Product Ratings\" program. The reviews are collected and compiled with reviews of the same products from other sources&nbsp;<b>(including \"Google Customer Reviews\" - see next paragraph - review aggregators, ...).<\/b>&nbsp;If conditions are met, the average product rating can then be displayed in your ads and free product listings in the form of one to five stars.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Finally, what better to encourage people to click and buy than a discount voucher featured in your ad? Thanks to our module you can filter and&nbsp;<b>export the promotional codes<\/b>&nbsp;to attach to your ads.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>(*)See conditions in the \"Features\" section<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><b>HIGHLIGHT THE QUALITY OF YOUR SERVICE WITH GOOGLE CUSTOMER REVIEWS<\/b><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The PRO version of the Google Merchant Center module integrates the \"Google Customer Reviews\" feature.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\"Google Customer Reviews\" is&nbsp;<b>a free service<\/b>&nbsp;that lets you collect, via Google,&nbsp;<b>your customers' reviews about their shopping experience.<\/b>&nbsp;If they agree to participate, they receive an email a few days after receiving their order, asking them to rate