 more.<\/li><\/ul><div><br><\/div><div><b>2. ChatGPT integration<\/b><\/div><div>We integrate ChatGPT, an advanced language model developed by OpenAI, into our powerful blogging solution. This innovative feature empowers administrators to effortlessly create compelling blog content by harnessing the capabilities of artificial intelligence. With ChatGPT at your fingertips, automatically crafting engaging titles, short descriptions, meta titles, meta descriptions, and blog post content becomes a seamless and efficient process.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The Blog module offers a time-saving prompt creation feature, empowering store admins to pre-define prompts to use for titles, content, and descriptions. No more repetitive tasks and streamline your blog creation process. With this feature, you can save valuable time and focus on crafting compelling content that drives engagement.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><b>3.\u00a0Beautiful and attractive design<\/b><\/div><ul><li><b>BLOG<\/b> comes with <b>4 layout templates<\/b> (grid, list, large box - grid, large box - list) designed with the latest design trends to make sure you have an eye-catching blog.<\/li><li><b>Unlimited colors<\/b> with color picker: Select suitable colors for your website from the back office using the color picker.<\/li><li><b>Fully responsive<\/b>: Displays perfectly on all devices\/screen sizes.<\/li><\/ul><div><br><\/div><div><b>4. Fully customizable<\/b><\/div><div>How to add a blog in PrestaShop? It's completely an easy task now! To help you build up your own unique and impressive PrestaShop blog, our <b>BLOG<\/b> module allows you to adjust every detail of each blog element, such as:<\/div><ul><li><b>Blog home page<\/b>: select how the blog post will be displayed, the number of blog posts, featured posts, and manage the featured gallery images, etc.<\/li><li><b>Blog sidebar<\/b>: set up sidebar position, type of blog post display on sidebar, which post block to display, etc.<\/li><li><b>Display blog posts on the product category page<\/b>: adjust the number of posts and select the type of display form (carousel slider or grid).<\/li><li><b>Image customization<\/b>: manage the size of various image types, for example, blog post thumbnail, main blog post image, category thumbnail, etc.<\/li><li><b>Table of contents<\/b>: creating a table of contents to help readers grasp the main content of a post and navigate to that position easily.<\/li><\/ul><div><br><\/div><div><b>5.\u00a0Image slider and gallery<\/b><\/div><ul><li><b>BLOG -<\/b> Best PrestaShop blog module comes with a beautiful image slider with attractive animation effects and many useful slider options to choose from, according to your preference.<\/li><li>You can set up a photo gallery page and display it on different positions on your website (main blog page, sidebar, etc.).<\/li><\/ul><div><br><\/div><div><b>6. Post author<\/b><\/div><div>Are you looking for some collaborators to be in charge of blog writing without interfering with your website management? Or maybe you just want to encourage your customers to contribute review articles and product introductions? With our blog module for PrestaShop - <b>BLOG<\/b>, you can <b>assign a group of customers to become blog authors<\/b> and give them certain privileges:<\/div><ul><li>Set status for an author. He\/she may be active, suspended, or suspended & hide posts.<\/li><li>Enable these authors to add, edit or delete a blog post.<\/li><li>Allow post authors to manage the comments from other customers on their posts.<\/li><\/ul><div><br><\/div><div><b>7.\u00a0SEO optimized<\/b><\/div><div>SEO optimization is one of the most important aspects of\u00a0<b>BLOG<\/b>. It\u2019s carefully checked to ensure your blog posts easily reach the first position on the search results page of the popular search engines (Google, Bing, etc.) with your SEO keywords.<\/div><ul><li><b>SEO Meta tags<\/b>: all Meta tags including Meta title, Meta keywords, Meta description are fully supported and are easy to manage.<\/li><li><b>SEO-friendly URL<\/b>: custom SEO-friendly URLs can be created to make your blog posts come up easily in Google keyword searches.<\/li><li><b>SEO-compatible HTML tags<\/b>: HTML tags are 100% compatible with the latest SEO standards to ensure your off-page SEO is perfect.<\/li><li><b>Google snippet supported<\/b>: displays structured data for posts in search results with rating, author, posting date, etc.<\/li><li><b>RSS feed<\/b>: provides your customers with better navigation, up-to-date information, and offers you some SEO value by increasing traffic that is generated as a result of your site is the place to go for information.<\/li><li><b>Google sitemap<\/b>: it helps visitors and Google bots find pages on the site. You can easily create one for your blog with our PrestaShop blog module.<\/li><\/ul><div><br><\/div><div><b>8.\u00a0Comments, likes, ratings, and poll<\/b><\/div><ul><li>Customers can comment, like, or rate a blog post on your website.<\/li><li>You can easily manage, track, and approve\/unapproved comments, likes, and ratings from customers via the module\u2019s backend.<\/li><li>Guest comments are supported. Customers can leave comments\/ratings on posts without having to register with your website.<\/li><li>Captcha security is also supported to make sure your blog comments are always real and not spam.<\/li><li><b>BLOG<\/b> allows you to add a poll on every blog post, you can enable the visitors to vote, use captcha security for polls, require feedback for polls, etc.<\/li><\/ul><div><br><\/div><div><b>9. Notification email<\/b><\/div><div><b>BLOG<\/b> comes with a <b>detailed email notification system<\/b>. Right after an event takes place, a notification email will be sent to you or your customers: when a new blog post is published, a new comment is posted or when a comment is reported, etc.<\/div><div>You can view and edit the notification email template that will be sent to administrators, authors, and users\/customers.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><b>10. Statistics<\/b><\/div><ul><li><b>BLOG<\/b> provides a detailed statistic tool for you. It has a chart to visualize your blog views, likes, and comments data with a time filter.<\/li><li>In addition, our module saves all the view log data such as your readers\u2019 IP addresses, web browsers, which post they read, etc. so you can have more insight information.<\/li><li><b>BLOG<\/b> also supports a clear log feature to save your server storage capacity.<\/li><\/ul><div><br><\/div><div><b>11.\u00a0Import and export content<\/b><\/div><ul><li>This is a unique feature that you only find in\u00a0<b>BLOG<\/b>, unlike other\u00a0free PrestaShop blog module It allows you to <b>export all your PrestaShop blog content<\/b> (blog posts, blog categories, slider images, and photo gallery) <b>in one click<\/b>.<\/li><li>You can also easily <b>import all the content to your blog in one click<\/b> soon after the PrestaShop blog integration with your website.<\/li><li>The <b>BLOG<\/b> module also allows you to import all the content from the <b>Simple Blog<\/b> module (a free PrestaShop blog module from PrestaHero).<\/li><li>You can <b>select types of data to import<\/b>: posts and categories, posts comments, slider images, gallery images, and module configuration. You can also select some suitable import options: override existing if exist the same ID, keep the post author ID or keep the commenter ID.<\/li><li><b>BLOG<\/b> enables you to <b>transfer data from WordPress<\/b> and this process can be done within a click \u2013 totally simple for everyone.<\/li><\/ul><div><br><\/div><div><b>12.\u00a0Flexibility & compatibility<\/b><\/div><ul><li><b>BLOG <\/b>is the most flexible\u00a0blog module for PrestaShop you may come across in the marketplace. Everything which appears on the front of the blog can be managed from its backend.<\/li><li>It is also coded with flexibility consideration using HTML, CSS, and PHP, so if you're a web developer you can easily customize the display of the blog according to your preference or extend its features if needed.<\/li><li>This module is strongly compatible with different versions of PrestaShop, custom themes and it\u2019s also guaranteed to work perfectly with other custom modules after\u00a0PrestaShop blog integration.<\/li><li><b>BLOG<\/b> is compatible with the most popular page builder modules such as <b>Creative Elements, CreativSlider<\/b>\u2026 and other Seo optimization modules: <b>SEO Audit, Awesome URLs, Pretty URLs, etc<\/b>.<\/li><\/ul><div><br><\/div><div><b>13.\u00a0Easy to use \u2013 backend<\/b><\/div><ul><li>Module backend is completely done with jQuery Ajax technology to reduce the number of page reloads when working with the backend. This helps you quickly manage your blog content (add, edit, delete, sort posts, change slider images, approve\/unapproved comments\/ratings, etc.)<\/li><li>The backend of\u00a0<b>BLOG<\/b> is simple and easy to manage even if you don\u2019t possess much technical knowledge.<\/li><\/ul><div><br><\/div><div><b>14.\u00a0Multi-shop, Multi-language, and RTL support<\/b><\/div><ul><li><b>BLOG <\/b>fully works with PrestaShop multi-shop mode, you can create separate blog posts, blog categories, etc. for each shop.<\/li><li><b>BLOG<\/b> is completely integrated with the default PrestaShop multi-language feature. You can easily translate everything from the back office to a language of preference.<\/li><\/ul><div><br><\/div><div>If your store is based in countries with right\u2013to\u2013left languages such as Arabic, Hebrew, Syrian, etc. this module is for you! We have taken a lot of care into making the front end of\u00a0<b>BLOG <\/b>fully support RTL languages.<\/div>","tab":"content_management","version":"4.5.5","compatibility":{"from":"1.6.0.4","to":"8.1.2"},"nbRates":"287","product_type":"module","avgRate":"4.8","price":{"EUR":97.99,"USD":114.99,"GBP":89.99},"badges":[{"label":"Modules Partner Creat