","displayName":"AliExpress Dropshipping - Product Importer ","categoryName":"Dropshipping","categoryId":"443","categoryParentName":"Specialized Platforms","categoryParentEnglishName":"Specialized Platforms","categoryParentId":"469","description":"AliExpress Dropshipping extension allows the shop owners to import products from AliExpress to their PrestaShop stores","author":"Webkul","url":"https:\/\/addons.prestashop.com\/en\/dropshipping\/29854-aliexpress-dropshipping-product-importer.html?utm_source=back-office&utm_medium=push-addons&utm_campaign=back-office-EN&utm_content=download","img":"https:\/\/medias1.prestastore.com\/img\/pico\/29854.jpg","fullDescription":"<div>AliExpress Dropshipping extension allows the shop owners to <b>import products from AliExpress<\/b> to their PrestaShop stores. Fulfill orders on AliExpress in a few clicks when someone places orders for imported products on PrestaShop store.<\/div>","additionalDescription":"<div><b>AliExpress Dropshipping module is compatible with PrestaShop version 8.x.x.<\/b><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Dropshipping is an eCommerce business model that allows you to sell products from your store without investing capital in inventory.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The PrestaShop Aliexpress Dropshipping module basically offers merchants the to <b>import products and their combinations from AliExpress into his\/her PrestaShop store<\/b>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>After that, they can start selling those products to the customers of the store. As there is no obligation to hold inventory so there is no limit to the number of products they can import from AliExpress.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Once the merchant receives an order on the PrestaShop, the <b>automatic ordering proces<\/b>s helps them to <b>place the order on Aliexpress with a single click<\/b>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>In order to import the product from AliExpress to PrestaShop, a chrome extension is needed. Follow the link to download the extension:<\/div