never again be limited in the analysis and understanding of your data.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div><b>NEW:<\/b> connect Op'art Stat and Op'art Devis together to get ten new metrics related to your quotes.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div><b>More than 80 metrics available for a 360-degree view of your data.<\/b><\/div><div>With more than 80 metrics available, the Op'art Stat module allows you to consult at a glance all the key indicators (KPIs) essential for your ecommerce.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>You will know where you stand at all times and will be able to easily follow the progress of your business.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div><b>Exceptional depth of analysis thanks to advanced filters<\/b><\/div><div>The Op'art Stat module not only provides numerous metrics, it also offers advanced filtering options that will allow you to achieve an extremely advanced level of analysis.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>Indeed, all the metrics offered by Op\u2019art stat can be filtered by: product, category, brand, customer group, country and payment method.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>These filters can be used as inclusion or exclusion filters, and can be combined for in-depth analysis.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>Using these filters, you can get incredibly accurate data. For example, you can analyze sales of a specific product in a particular country, or understand the purchasing behavior of a group of customers using a certain payment method.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>You can also exclude certain categories or brands to focus on the data that is most relevant to you and eliminate \u201cparasite data\u201d that alter your statistics.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>Such precision in your data allows you to understand exactly what is happening in your business, spot trends and specific issues, and make decisions based on accurate information.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div><b>Track specific data with tailored metrics.<\/b><\/div><div>We know that each e-commerce has its own specificities. This is why the Op\u2019art Stat module offers the possibility of creating personalized metrics, for an analysis that perfectly matches your needs.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>This advanced functionality allows you to extract and integrate any relevant data directly into the module.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>You can even integrate data from an external service directly into the module.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>Warning: Adding custom metrics requires some coding skills. If you work with an agency, they will be able to add these metrics for you very simply and we can do this for you as well.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div><b>Complete report customization for views tailored to your needs.<\/b><\/div><div>The Op'art Stat module emphasizes customization, allowing you to choose precisely which metrics to display on each report and their order of appearance.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>With the variety of reports available and filtering options, you have the freedom to create views that meet your exact needs.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>Whether you want a report focused on traffic, finances, or any other aspect of your e-commerce, Op'art Stat gives you the possibility to do so and you can of course create a report with the key figures you wish to consult daily.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>You can create, duplicate, and delete reports with a single click.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thus, if you want to easily follow the sales evolution of a given category, brand or product, you just need to create a report with the corresponding filters to access its data in one click.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div><b>Ideal for teamwork.<\/b><\/div><div>Op'art Stat facilitates teamwork by allowing each member to benefit from all the customization features.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>Each team member can create their own reports, tailored to their needs.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>The sales manager can create reports focused on sales by product and region, while the marketing manager can focus on metrics related to advertising campaigns. Likewise, the financial director may have reports dedicated to the financial aspects of the company, etc.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>Thus, each member of the team has a clear and precise view of the information that is relevant to them, thus facilitating decision-making and collaboration.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div><b>An autonomous module independent of any external solution.<\/b><\/div><div>Op'art Stat is a standalone module that does not need any other module to works.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>It also does not use Google Analytics or any other external services.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>You can therefore, if you wish, get rid of these additional modules and only use Op'art Stat for all your analyses.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>You simplify the management of your e-commerce by reducing the number of modules that you must use and update regularly.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>With Op'art Stat, you have a unique and powerful tool that meets all your analysis needs, allowing you to focus on what really matters: the growth of your business.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div><b>Fast display and maintenance of your site's performance.<\/b><\/div><div>Op\u2019art stat is designed to offer optimal performance. With optimized queries and asynchronous loading, it quickly displays all your metrics. (The module has been tested on stores with more than 100,000 products and 50,000 orders without encountering any problems.)<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>Unlike certain statistics modules which can slow down your store by recording too much information in the database, Op'art Stat has been designed to preserve the performance of your PrestaShop.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>In fact, 90% of the data used by the module is already present in your Prestashop and will never be modified.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>For the remaining 10% of data, it is monitored and automatically limited by our module. (This limit can be modified by the merchant in the module configuration).<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div><b>Immediate access to your data history<\/b><\/div><div>You have access to all your data history as soon as the module is installed. Only traffic data starts accumulating from the day of installation.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div><b>Live data<\/b><\/div><div>Op'art Stat offers a \"Live\" table which provides real-time data on your store. It is a valuable tool for tracking the instant activity of your e-commerce and the behavior of your users.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div><b>Monitoring marketing campaigns<\/b><\/div><div>Thanks to URL markers (utm), effectively monitor your marketing campaigns and obtain detailed data on their performance and their impact on your e-commerce.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div><b>Comparative temporal and filter analysis<\/b><\/div><div>Of course, Op'art Stat offers the possibility of comparing different periods. But you can also compare different filters.<\/div><div>For example, you can compare the sales of two products or two categories over the same period.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div><b>Compatible multi-boutique.<\/b><\/div><div>The module is multi-store compatible, so you can consult the figures for each of your stores or look at the cumulative statistics of all your stores.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><b>Export your data in one click.<\/b><\/div><div>You can get standard CSV exports in one click and integrate your data into any spreadsheet or software.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div><b>Premium after-sales service and more than 10 years of experience<\/b><\/div><div>Selling modules is not a secondary activity for us, it is our only activity!<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>Therefore, we put 100% of our energy into providing you with quality modules and after-sales service that meets your expectations.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div><div>Our 10 years of experience in creating and maintaining PrestaShop modules allow us, if necessary, to intervene quickly and without risk on your store.<\/div><div>&nbsp;<\/div>","tab":"analytics_stats","version":"3.1.32","compatibility":{"from":"1.6.0.4","to":"8.1.2"},"nbRates":"0","product_type":"module","avgRate":"0.0","price":{"EUR":111.99,"USD":129.99,"GBP":97.99},"badges":[{"label":"Modules Partner Creator","img":"https:\/\/medias2.prestastore.com\/themes\/prestastore\/img\/front\/sprites\/badges\/module-editor.png"}],"cover":{"small":"https:\/\/addons.prestashop.com\/1575583-pprod\/opart-stat-reliable-and-useful-ecommerce-statistics.jpg","big":"https:\/\/addons.prestashop.com\/1575583-pbig\/opart-stat-reliable-and-useful-ecommerce-statistics.jpg"},"changeLog":{"1.0.19":["First upload"],"1.0.24":[" Bug fixed : extension undefined index extension"," Add validator security and licence requirement"],"1.0.28":["Licence added to apexchart library files"],"1.0.32":["Licences changed"],"1.0.38":["Compatibility prestashop 8","Compatibility problem fixed for prestashop 1.7.5.0"],"1.0.41":["We don't use statut update date anymore, we are using the invoce_date"],"1.0.46":["Save preselected period feature enhanced","Now a search engine can help to find quickly the desired reports","Max visit limit added in config form","OpartStat can now use product cost for each product variation to calculate the profit","Blank robot name are not allowed"],"1.0.53":["Average revenu per day and average revenue per day trend reports added"],"1.0.59":["marginCoefficient and marginCoefficientTrend reports added","MarginRate, marginRateTrend, bestMarginCoefficientProduct, bestRevenuesPerVisitProduct reports added","table prefix missing for bestrevenuespervisitproduct report","Display bug fixed when url was too long in besttraficpage report","translation missing + compare bug fixed for bestrevenuepervisitproduct report"],"2.0.0":["OpartStat can now be linked with external module to get usefull statistics"],"2.0.":["Index.php file add to some directories"],"2.0.6":["isFileName security Added  on getJsonConfig me